sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Cliente (React)
    participant G as API Gateway (Nginx)
    participant S as Community Service (C++)
    participant O as ONNX Runtime (C++)
    participant P as PostgreSQL
    participant R as Redis
    participant KF as Kafka

    C->>G: POST /community/posts (title, content, tags, imageUrl)
    G->>S: Proxy → /community/posts
    
    Note over S: Extraer userId del token JWT
    
    S->>O: POST /embed (texts: [title+content+tags])
    O-->>S: embedding (384 dimensiones)
    
    S->>P: INSERT INTO posts (user_id, title, content, tags, embedding)
    P-->>S: postId, created_at
    
    S->>R: DEL community:posts:list:* (invalidar caché)
    S->>R: DEL community:personalized:feed:{userId}
    S->>R: DEL community:trending:posts:*
    
    S->>KF: Produce evento "post_created" (topic: community-events)
    
    S-->>C: 201 Created (postId, message)